Each rofpin is a yumpus. Every storpist is a shalpist. Each shilpant is a rofpin. Each harpin is a storpist. Harpins are not round. Each fimple is a harpin. Dropants are fimples. Chorpers are dropants. Every zilpor is a chorper. Parpers are zilpors. Tumpuses are zilpors. Porpors are parpers. Gorpees are parpers. Daumpins are porpors. Daumpins are not hard. Each fomple is a daumpin. Every fomple is metallic. Sam is a parper.
